               <msContents>
                  <summary>Säwasǝw, Ge‘ez Vocabulary and Grammar, explained in Amharic, ሰዋስወ፡ ግእዝ፡, Office Prayers, fragment</summary>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez" otherLangs="am">Gǝ‘ǝz and Amharic</textLang>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="59r" facs="003">Fols 1r–59r</locus><title><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2293Sawase">Sawāsǝw (general
                                                  record)</title> explained in Amharic</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ንዌጥን፡ በረድኤተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ጽሕፈተ፡ አናቅጽ፡ ዘአስተጋብእዎሙ፡ መምህራን፡ እምኵሉ፡ መጻሕት። ሎሀ፡ ጻፈ፡ ላህልሀ፡ ነከረ:</incipit></msItem>
